    "spark plugs": "MBClub UK and W212 enthusiast guides cite spark plug renewal around 50,000 km or 4 years for performance V8 models; 50,000 km / 48 months used here as a conservative EU-oriented interval for direct-injection petrol engines—verify AMG M156 variants in your booklet.",
